Header: 65-year-old male stabbed to death in Galgamuwa
Content: Colombo (News 1st) – A person has been stabbed to death with a sharp object in the Dalupothagama village in Galgamuwa. The 65-year-old male victim had died while being transported to the Anuradhapura base hospital. A suspect is now in custody. Investigation are currently underway.
